## ğŸ“Š Expanded Durability & Degradation Table

| **Material**        | **Degradation Mechanism**       | **Approx. Rate**          | **Estimated Time to Structural Failure** | **Long-Term Behavior** |
|---------------------|----------------------------------|----------------------------|------------------------------------------|-------------------------|
| **Titanium (Grade 2)**     | None (passive oxide layer)       | ~0.00001 mm/year           | **100,000â€“300,000+ years**               | Essentially eternal in this setting |
| **Bronze**          | Patina (copper oxide), slow pitting | ~0.0001â€“0.0005 mm/year     | **5,000â€“10,000 years**                   | Gradual erosion, keeps core structure |
